name: The Space Gnome's Guide To Good Rocks
name_original: The Space Gnome's Guide To Good Rocks
description:
This is the Three Rocks divination guide for 2021, for my Patreon and Discord subscribers.

To generate your gnome divination for the year, please prepare three rocks, wrapped in fabric or paper. 

To support me on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/shing

To join the Friends of the Space Gnome Discord: https://discord.gg/5f3C347
